          </li>

          <div class="item">
            <img class="maker" src="https://launchpass-production.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/user/profile_photo/2621/IMG_9961.jpg" alt="jordan"/>
            <span class="caption">Jordan Chu</span>
          </div>

          <li>
            <a class="creator" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/jordanchu1995/"><i class="fa fa-linkedin-square fa-2x" aria-hidden="true"></i></a>
